    public class QueryAllApiKey
extends AbstractQueryAllApiKey

    An all-object query of a ApiKey using its primary key. This class is the concrete subclass of the generated abstract class AbstractQueryAllApiKey.

    Make any changes to query behavior by overriding methods here rather than changing the abstract superclass; AndroMDA will overwrite that class when you run it but will never overwrite this concrete subclass.

    This class contains the specification of the SQL statement that queries all the ApiKey objects in the database. Use caution with this query.
